From Geoff Filinuk Subject Selfish hockey On Tuesday when it was raining in Chicago ESPN provided bonus hockey Now it seems as though some fans are ticked off that the NY Wash OT was replaced with the Angels People must realize that there are more baseball fans instead of hockey fans in the The baseball game was scheduled to air and advertisers money was paid so they can't skip the baseball Why don't you people CHILL OUT and enjoy whatever coverage you can Geoff Filinuk